caption_bersih:
from china to pik 2 .
chu chat akhirnya buka di pik 2, pelopor sea salt ice tea sejak 2016. lokasinya ada di samping taman doa lady of akita, pik 2. yang bikin beda: packaging-nya super elegant & mewah, dan tiap menu pun punya desain kemasan yang beda. tehnya wangi banget, rasa semua minumannya balanced kalo disini pesen normal sugar aja udah pas, ga manis .
mereka pakai teh fresh brew yang diganti setiap 4 jam sekali, jadi kualitasnya selalu terjaga. no wonder rasanya enak dan clean! jangan lewatkan grand opening promo buy 1 get 1 + free merch di 2730 november 2025
.
highly recommended buat langsung cobain
alamat_resolved: PIK 2 Next to Taman Doa Lady of Akita
caption_no_cta:
from china to pik 2 . chu chat akhirnya buka di pik 2, pelopor sea salt ice tea sejak 2016. lokasinya ada di samping taman doa lady of akita, pik 2. yang bikin beda: packaging-nya super elegant & mewah, dan tiap menu pun punya desain kemasan yang beda. tehnya wangi banget, rasa semua minumannya balanced kalo disini pesen normal sugar aja udah pas, ga manis . mereka pakai teh fresh brew yang diganti setiap 4 jam sekali, jadi kualitasnya selalu terjaga. no wonder rasanya enak dan clean! jangan lewatkan grand opening promo buy 1 get 1 + free merch di 2730 november 2025
.

alamat_resolved: Jl. Taman Aries No.8, Eco8, Puri, Jakarta Barat

caption:
thai flavors duo chef collaboration ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡­
.
thai flavors taken to the next level with a special collaboration between chef @freddiesalim of @silkthaijkt and chef louis tikaram @the_lou_dad from brisbane
.

caption:
one of the newest resorts in pererenan, @noema.resort is just a three-minute walk from the beach. it offers a unique mix of tropical tranquility and community spirit
.
we stayed in the beautifully designed tropical lagoon studio twin. the resort features a gallery, swimming pool, gym, and playground area
.
for dining, @mamalomarestaurant serves all-day fusion dishes combining asian, local, and international flavors. we especially enjoyed the indonesian menu at @paparempa , including sate bakar, lombok short ribs, and timbungan-style duck
.
a perfect staycation spot in pererenanâ¤µï¸
.

.
